Package: nmatools
Title: Network Meta-Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yuki", "Furukawa", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Wrapper functions for network meta-analysis using the netmeta package.
    Provides one-stop functions for running NMA, saving outputs (text, RDS, CSV,
    league tables), and generating trimmed, A4-ready forest plots with automatic
    subnetwork detection and page splitting for large plots.
